o Deduction: Providing rigorous verification and judgment.

Conclusion: The Eternal Path of AGI

LLM brings the ultimate induction.

Mind Model represents the ultimate in deduction.

Induction is like the sea, deduction is like a sword.

The sea embraces all rivers without losing its breadth;

The sword cuts through doubt without losing its accuracy.

When Yin and Yang complement each other, and induction and deduction reinforce each other, artificial intelligence will no longer merely imitate knowledge, but truly understand it; it will no longer simply generate answers, but verify them; it will no longer be just a tool, but a reliable intelligent partner.

The eternal path of AGI lies not in Yin, nor in Yang, but in their unity.

(Core Formula)

AGI = Induction (Statistics) + Deduction (Reasoning)

Intelligence = Experience × Logic

Reliability = Correlation + Causality

The Eternal Path = Yin and Yang Interdependence

Only through the harmony of Yin and Yang can we reach the true "eternal path."
